Christmas Decorations
        §4Ka Studios

§2How to play?
§0This add-on adds new winter decorations to your Minecraft world, each with special features, you can find vehicles, clothes, lights and much more!

§4Sleigh Spruce
§0This sleigh will help you move faster in your world!
§2how to craft?
§0on your crafting table:
[ ]  [#]  [L]
[#]  [S]  [#]
[ ]  [ ]  [ ]

"#": Spruce Fence
"L": Lever
"S": Spruce_Planks

§4Golden Sleigh
§0This vehicle is faster and you can use it with two people maximum.
§2how to craft?
§0on your crafting table:
[#]  [G]  [#]
[G]  [g]  [G]
[ ]  [ ]  [ ]

"#": Red Wool
"G": Gold Block
"g": Gold Ingot

§4Iron Sleigh
§0This is the fastest and most durable transport!
§2how to craft?
§0on your crafting table: 
[#]  [ ]  [ ]
[R]  [T]  [G]
[i]  [ ]  [i]
"#": Iron Block
"R": Redstone
"T": Red Wool
"G": Glass,"i": Iron Ingot
